ZH: 今天的退潮时间是下午三点。
EN: Today's ebb tide is at 3 PM.

ZH: 游客们喜欢在退潮时来海滩玩耍。
EN: Tourists like to play on the beach during ebb tide.

ZH: 那个渔民知道什么时候是最好的退潮时间。
EN: That fisherman knows the best time for ebb tide.

ZH: 退潮时，岩石和贝壳暴露在海滩上。
EN: During ebb tide, rocks and shells are exposed on the beach.

ZH: 早上的退潮给我们带来了一个漂亮的日出景色。
EN: The early ebb tide brought us a beautiful sunrise.

ZH: 退潮之后，我们会开始捡贝壳。
EN: After the ebb tide, we will start picking up seashells.

ZH: 当退潮开始，沙滩上出现了很多浅水湖。
EN: When the ebb tide starts, many shallow pools appear on the beach.

ZH: 退潮时，渔民们会钓很多鱼。
EN: During ebb tide, fishermen catch a lot of fish.

ZH: 退潮的时候，我们可以看到海底的一些生物。
EN: During ebb tide, we can see some creatures on the seafloor.

ZH: 海鸟在退潮时在海滩上觅食。
EN: Seabirds forage on the beach during ebb tide.

ZH: 看到退潮的时候，我就知道是时候去捡贝壳了。
EN: When I see the ebb tide, I know it's time to pick up seashells.

ZH: 退潮时，浪花消失了。
EN: During ebb tide, the waves disappear.

ZH: 游泳是不安全的时候是退潮时。
EN: Swimming is unsafe during ebb tide.

ZH: 许多鱼类会跟随退潮，离开潮汐区。
EN: Many fish follow the ebb tide and leave the tidal area.

ZH: 退潮后的沙滩上，留下了波浪的痕迹。
EN: The waves leave marks on the beach after ebb tide.

ZH: 退潮时，浅水区变浅了。
EN: During ebb tide, the shallow water area becomes shallower.

ZH: 看到海水渐渐退去，我知道退潮开始了。
EN: Seeing the seawater gradually recede, I know ebb tide has started.

ZH: 黄昏时的退潮时刻让人感到宁静和平静。
EN: The ebb tide moment at dusk brings a sense of tranquility and calmness.

ZH: 退潮后，有很多贝壳和海藻留在沙滩上。
EN: After ebb tide, many shells and seaweeds are left on the beach.

ZH: 长时间的退潮会暴露出海底的珊瑚礁。
EN: Long periods of ebb tide expose the underwater coral reefs.
